snippet.title: Amber Heard Admits to Being Abusive
snippet.description:
She even has people signing petitions to protect her, and corporations like L'Oréal calling her an inspiration.

The full audio is all over YouTube. Pictures of Johnny Depp's injuries and the videos of Amber lying in and out of court are also easy to find. Hell, in this video, she even lays out her plot to lie about being abused! So there's plenty to show these "I Stand With Amber Heard" and "We Stand With Amber Heard" clowns.

Please sign the petition to have Amber Heard fired from Aquaman 2. Here's the link:

http://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

This link shows 343 studies proving that females -- including teens -- are just as abusive as men towards their partners, if not more:

https://bit.ly/3fmbt7P

Here are a few support systems for abused men:

http://www.oneinthree.com.au

http://www.shrink4men.com

#phenoMENalAct #JusticeForJohnnyDepp #FireAmberHeard
